      "covers": [
        "moon build --target llvm"
      ],
      "reason": "outcome differs by install channel (verified 2026-07-17): on the stable/latest channel moon build --target llvm fails (internal compiler error, exit 255); on the nightly channel it builds with a warning that LLVM is experimental. No single exit-code expectation holds across CI lanes, so this entry documents rather than runs."
